709727f-a.text:
Seventh Avenue, north across W. 26th Street, shosing mainly the easterly side. Note the newly completed 21-story loft and offices structure at the Y. E. corner of 27th Street. The 20story Manufacturers Building occupies the 28th and 29th Street frontage. The Pennsylvania Hotel is the next large unit observable. At the lower left is 8uffantis Restaurant at the S. W. Corner.
April 10, 1921
Gift of E. W. Jenks
